    <p class="eyebrow">All about me</p>
    <h2>A personal corner of the internet.</h2>
    <div class="about-photo">
      <img src="/assets/images/profile/portrait-smile.jpg" alt="Tanyaradzwa smiling">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="about-copy">
    <p>Welcome to Tanya’s little corner. I am someone who genuinely loves IT and anything software-related. Through my content, I want to help people understand that IT is bigger than coding, fixing computers or being a technician.</p>
    <p>There are so many powerful roles in tech, from testing and business analysis to databases, support, systems thinking and more. I want to make those paths feel easier to understand, especially for people who are still trying to find where they fit.</p>
    <p>Outside of IT, I enjoy travelling, going to church, reading my Bible, cooking, baking, music, playing guitar and spending time around farming and nature. I will not be sharing everything about my life, but I will share interesting parts of the things I love, what I am learning and the journey I am walking.</p>
  </div>
</section>

